Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:41.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even when wounded and made to suffer,\nhe is reborn and gets right back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Youth, what a formidable\nthing it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:49.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, our resolve to have our vengeance\nwill shatter even that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our grip on the reins will never loosen,\nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.01,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Act 20:\NFarewell, Eugenie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:12.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur. This arrived\nfrom Baron Danglars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:19.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:25.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This says that the signing ceremony for\NEugenie's wedding will be held tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must really be in rough\nfinancial shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's rushing his\ndaughter's wedding like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This won't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:04.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you lost your pride the same\ninstant that you lost your status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want about me,\nbut you ARE gonna let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:15.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the princess is in a\nbit of a foul mood at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She even did this\nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you\ndo to Eugenie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:26.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?\NAfter all, we're to be man and wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She put up some fierce\nresistance, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:34.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, I didn't do anything as barbaric\nas forcing myself on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I told her,\N"By marrying me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"...you'll not only be safeguarding\nthe lifestyle of your own family,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:45.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"...but also that of the Morcerf,\nno, the Mondego family."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:49.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The instant I mentioned your name,\nshe started behaving herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:56.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a debt of gratitude.\NYou're our sacred Cupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will go off without\na hitch, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about\NCavalcanti's activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going\naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about.\NPlease get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NYou may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humiliation and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those will be my gifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to my beloved father\nand mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:23.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as my\nlittle sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle, you look\nso lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I wearing\na dress like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:13.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Today's affair will just be a\nsigning ceremony attended only by family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I think it would be best\nfor you to wear your formal gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a little girl, I\nnever enjoyed talking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I never!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie! Look at you,\nyou're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It really does look wonderful on you.\NAndrea will be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be alone\nuntil the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, of course.\NGo ahead and do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, things are going\nto become quite hectic soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. With him in the family,\nwe've got nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's young, but that boy\nhas nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:07:00.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your performance at the opera house\nwas most impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:07.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For me, meeting fresh, young talent is a joy\nthat I would not trade for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:14.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you are interested, would you care\nto come to our conservatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Signed, F. Damrosch,\NHead Instructor of Keyboard Instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Danglars is a\nslick customer, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:39.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to show everyone that the Danglars\nfamily's financial situation has stabilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...by inviting his stockholders and having us\ncover his daughter's wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:47.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because he'll be in effective control\nof Marquis Cavalcanti's fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The real question is, what's\NAlbert going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think he's\ngonna show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:55.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here. He's not a member\nof the aristocracy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means\nhe's free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:24.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2}I couldn't disobey Luigi.\NHe's like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:30.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to forgive me.\NBut at least let me do something to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:35.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it up to here with people\njerking me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:51.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you want to save the girl you love,\NI want to help the boy I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here comes\nthe bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie, you have no idea how long\NI've waited for this day to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:05.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well,\nlet us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:12.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, we will now\ncarry out the signing of the vows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...between Eugenie de Danglars\nand Andrea Cavalcanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will begin with\nthe groom-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:25.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have no objections to sharing\nall property, bonds, stocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:31.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and other assets in your possession\nwith Eugenie, your bride-to-be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:37.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please place your signature\non the marriage contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And now, Eugenie,\nthe bride-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:48.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have no objections to sharing\nall property, bonds, stocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:53.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and other assets in your possession\nwith your groom-to-be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:10.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Eugenie?!\NHurry up and answer the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't\nseem right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will repeat the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:23.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have no objections to sharing\nall property, bonds, stocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:28.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and other assets in your possession\nwith your groom-to-be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:35.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, she seems\nto be extremely nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, she has\nno objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danglars must really\nbe desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Sign the contract,\NEugenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:04.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I forgot to pay\nthe power bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:46.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Marie Antoinette, the wife of\NLouis XVI, who ruled during the Middle Ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...spilled ink onto their marriage contract\nduring the signing ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:56.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as if hinting at the misfortune\nthat would later befall her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:07.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This stain is saying the same thing.\NI'd reconsider if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!\NWho put you up to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody put me up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.80,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't approve\nof this wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:19.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! You don't work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! What do you think you're...\NCut the crap! You don't work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but this is too good\na scoop to pass up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, you bastard!\NGive me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:46.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Danglars, I think that he's\nthe least of your worries right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are the police\ndoing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Andrea Cavalcanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest on charges of fraud,\nfalsification of lineage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...larceny, rape, as well\nas six other offenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:03.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, you bastards!\NLet go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth,\nyou fake aristocrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fake aristocrat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shove it, you miser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...\NI was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My revenge isn't\nover yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about, Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!\NW-What are you talking about, Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Eugenie, let's go!\NTogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You two are sneaking in\nthrough that hole again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I secretly weakened it last night.\NI made it big enough for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd completely forgotten\nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your chariot awaits, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Renaud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reports say that Cavalcanti\nhas been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:31.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bertuccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For I no longer sleep,\nyou see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:50.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In its place, I had this golden\nbox garden constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:56.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But now, this room is the only place\nin which I may remain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:02.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And this single glass of water\ncomprises my entire fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:08.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what of you? What do you intend\nto do once all of this is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:16.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I dream of... is to\nserve you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that dream\ncan never be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there is no one but Your Excellency\nthat I can serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:29.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When this is over, my wealth will\nbelong to you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Use it in the pursuit\nof your own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bankruptcy means nothing to me!\NI still have money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run, and run,\nand keep on running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:52.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!\NI'll escape all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:04.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boarding procedures for flight 747\nto New York are almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All boarding passengers, please\nreport to the boarding gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.67,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You go first, Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can go first, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the\nway I've acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was always thinking\nof myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never gave a second thought\nto your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:40.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, no matter what happens,\nno matter where I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll always be in\nmy thoughts, Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:47.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert... You'll always be\nin mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:12.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flight 747 to New York will\nbe departing momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers intending to board, please\nproceed to gate 4 immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever things get tough,\NI want you to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The piano that I love\nto hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be thinking\nof you when I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Show those guys in\NNew York how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:47.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flight 747 to New York\nwill be departing momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, Eugenie's flight\ntook off okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from Eugenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:04.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She said that she had it in the\nbodice of her dress the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To my dearest Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:15.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you read this, chances are\nthat I'll no longer be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of giving you a present,\NI'd like you to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:25.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, this is important. I don't\nwant you to ever hate anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something occurred\nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:34.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings of love and feelings of hate\nboth start out as caring about someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:40.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad, but I think that sometimes,\nwhen those feelings aren't returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...those feelings of love\nchange into hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:48.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If something like that ever happens, I want\nyou to think back to our childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back to a time when we could\nonly love openly and honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how often\nwe got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to\ngo on living, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:03.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love people openly without\nbeing scared of getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I truly was lucky\nto have known you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz d'Epinay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:15.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forever in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have to see him\none more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:37.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I have\nto talk to him about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:12.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny.\NAnd revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The merciless gears\nkeep turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I once again find myself\nstanding before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 21...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.54,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Act 21:\NThe Golden Boy's True Identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:22.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."The Golden Boy's True Identity."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
